sentence: i need a round trip flight from cincinnati to san jose california
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.airport_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',

 '"'||v5.state_name||'"', '"'||v6.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v7.fare_id||'"', v7.round_trip_cost FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
